The death toll from Tuesday's Bahati killer brew has risen to 8 after 3 more people died today while undergoing treatment, the three include 7-month pregnant Lucy Nyambura, whose family tells of the lady&rsquo;s struggle with alcoholism since her husband died several years ago. Two others were today traced and are receiving treatment at the rift valley provincial general hospital. Five people are still unaccounted for. Ibrahim Karanja reports on yesterday's tragic events that struck Hodi Hodi village in Bahati.